# Map the @schoen scope to the Gitea npm registry so CI's `npx @schoen/aislop`
# pulls the prebuilt C#-capable aislop tarball (anonymous read; no token).
# Why a published tarball and not the github.com/mtschoen/aislop fork directly:
# on the host-mode act_runner, `npm install` of the fork runs its tsdown/postinstall
# build, which is POSIX-only and fails on the runner. See local-ci
# project-ci-setup.md "Trap 2".
@schoen:registry=https://gitea.llamabox.sticktoitive.net/api/packages/schoen/npm/
